{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-127-abc-hits","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-101-to-200","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba iz 127: abc-hits","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Radikal broja $n$, $rad(n)$, je proizvod različitih prostih činilaca $n$. Na primer, $504 = 2^3 × 3^2 × 7$, stoga $rad(504) = 2 × 3 × 7 = 42$.</p>\n<p>Objasnićemo triplet pozitivnih celih brojeva (a, b, c) da je abc-triple ako:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>$GCD(a, b) = GCD(a, c) = GCD(b, c) = 1$</li>\n<li>$a &#x3C; b$</li>\n<li>$a + b = c$</li>\n<li>rad(abc) &#x3C; c$</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Primer, (5, 27, 32) je abc-hit, jer:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>$GCD(5, 27) = GCD(5, 32) = GCD(27, 32) = 1$</li>\n<li>$5 &#x3C; 27$</li>\n<li>$5 + 27 = 32$</li>\n<li>$rad(4320) = 30 &#x3C; 32$</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Izgleda da su abc-hits veoma retki/riđak, i ima samo trideset i jedna abc-hits za $c &#x3C; 1000$, a $\\sum{c} = 12523$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $\\sum{c}$ za $c &#x3C; 120000$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f3ec1000cf542c50fefe","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301754,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-101-to-200/problem-127-abc-hits"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function abcHits() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nabcHits();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>abcHits()</code> trebalo bi vratiti <code>18407904</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(abcHits(), 18407904);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-101-to-200","dashedName"